# BitCalm Client
Automatically backup your Linux server files &amp; databases  to Amazon S3 cloud and restore it by 1 click. No sysadmin required.


# How it works
1. Installation in 30 seconds. Install BitCalm opensource client on your server
2. Configuration in 30 seconds. Configure files and DB auto backup settings
3. One click data restore. Easily restore your server data from any backup version

Help: https://bitcalm.com/help/
